&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Job Overview&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The ParkX Porter is responsible for maintaining cleanliness in the common areas at assigned sites. Duties include general upkeep such as pressure washing, window cleaning, trash removal, and routine cleaning tasks. Porter also support event setup and cleanup when necessary and respond to cleanliness concerns as they arise. The position requires reliability, attention to detail, and the ability to work professionally and courteously with property staff, tenants, and visitors.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
